gn13": null, "ArabicBlueSign13": null, "ArabicText14": null, "ArabicGreenSign14": null, "ArabicRedSign14": null, "ArabicBlueSign14": null, "ArabicText15": null, "ArabicGreenSign15": null, "ArabicRedSign15": null, "ArabicBlueSign15": null, "ArabicText16": null, "ArabicGreenSign16": null, "ArabicRedSign16": null, "ArabicBlueSign16": null, "ArabicText17": null, "ArabicGreenSign17": null, "ArabicRedSign17": null, "ArabicBlueSign17": null, "ArabicText18": null, "ArabicGreenSign18": null, "ArabicRedSign18": null, "ArabicBlueSign18": null, "ArabicText19": null, "ArabicGreenSign19": null, "ArabicRedSign19": null, "ArabicBlueSign19": null, "ArabicText20": null, "ArabicGreenSign20": null, "ArabicRedSign20": null, "ArabicBlueSign20": null, "EnglishImage": null, "GujaratiImage": null, "RUrduImage": null, "UrduImage": null, "IsRed": 0, "MinimizeDescriptionLine": 0, "IsPrintable": 0}, {"Id": 1016815, "EnglishTitle": null, "GujaratiTitle": null, "RUrduTitle": null, "UrduTitle": null, "Sequence": null, "EnglishDescription": "Whoever recites this supplication (3) three times in the morning shall be rescued from drowning, burnt and theft till the evening period, and whoever recite it (3) three times in the evening shall be rescued from burnt, drowning and theft till morning period. Verily Khidr and Ilyas (a) usually meet in every occasion and departed each other with these very words. This is the slogans of my followers which differentiate them from my enemies when the Qa'im shall be coming out.", "GujaratiDescription": null, "RUrduDescription": "Jo bhi is dua ko subh ke waqt 3 martaba padhe to woh doobne, jalne aur chori se shab tak mehfooz hai aur jo bhi usey raat mein 3 martaba padhe woh subh tak mazkoorah (upar di huwi teeno) cheezo se mehfooz rahega. Hazrat Khizr (a) aur Ilyaas (a) har saal Hajj mein ek-dusre se mulaqaat karte hai aur ek-dusre se rukhsat hote waqt in kalemaat ko padhte hai yeh hamare Shiyo’n ka tariqah hai, jis roz hamare Qaaem (a) ka zahoor hoga, usi ke zariye hamare chahne waale aur dushman pehchaane jaayenge.", "UrduDescription": "جو بھی اس دعا کو صبح کے وقت تین مرتبہ پڑھے غرق ہونے جلنے اور چوری سے محفوظ ہوگا رات تک اور جو بھی اس دعا کو تین مرتبہ رات کے وقت پڑھے صبح تک اس سے امان میں رہے گا۔ اور خضر اور الیاس ہر سال حج کے موقع پر آپس میں ملاقات کرتے ہیں اور ایکدوسرے سے جدا ہوتے وقت یہ کلمات پڑھتے ہیں اور یہ دعا میرے شیعوں کا شعار ہے اور اس دعا کی وجہ سے دشمنوں کو ہمارے دوستوں سے جب قائم آل محمد قیام کرے گا تو اس وقت پہچانا جائے گ۔", "English": null, "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": null, "Urdu": null, "RArabic": null, "ArabicText1": null, "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": null, "ArabicBlueSign3": null, "ArabicText4": null, "ArabicGreenSign4": null, "ArabicRedSign4": null, "ArabicBlueSign4": null, "ArabicText5": null, "ArabicGreenSign5": null, "ArabicRedSign5": null, "ArabicBlueSign5": null, "ArabicText6": null, "ArabicGreenSign6": null, "ArabicRedSign6": null, "ArabicBlueSign6": null, "ArabicText7": null, "ArabicGreenSign7": null, "ArabicRedSign7": null, "ArabicBlueSign7": null, "ArabicText8": null, "ArabicGreenSign8": null, "ArabicRedSign8": null, "ArabicBlueSign8": null, "ArabicText9": null, "ArabicGreenSign9": null, "ArabicRedSign9": null, "ArabicBlueSign9": null, "ArabicText10": null, "ArabicGreenSign10": null, "ArabicRedSign10": null, "ArabicBlueSign10": null, "ArabicText11": null, "ArabicGreenSign11": null, "ArabicRedSign11": null, "ArabicBlueSign11": null, "ArabicText12": null, "ArabicGreenSign12": null, "ArabicRedSign12": null, "ArabicBlueSign12": null, "ArabicText13": null, "ArabicGreenSign13": null, "ArabicRedSign13": null, "ArabicBlueSign13": null, "ArabicText14": null, "ArabicGreenSign14": null, "ArabicRedSign14": null, "ArabicBlueSign14": null, "ArabicText15": null, "ArabicGreenSign15": null, "Ar